No. 11-338. Doug Decker, in His Official Capacity as Oregon State Forester, et al., Petitioners v. Northwest Environmental Defense Center. Georgia-Pacific West, Inc., et al., Petitioners v. Northwest Environmental Defense Center. No. 11-347. 565 U.S. 1091, 132 S. Ct. 865,

181 L. Ed. 2d 547,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8836. December 12, 2011.

The Solicitor General is invited to file a brief in these cases expressing the views of the United States.

Justice Breyer took no part in the consideration or decision of these petitions.

Same cases below, 640 F.3d 1063.
